HEADWORD: Bowknot
<hw>Bow"knot`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A knot in which a
portion of the string is drawn through in the form of a loop or bow, so
as to be readily untied.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

